room_title: Escape room "The Twisted Curse of Madame Antinori" by Time Trapped Escape Room in Tampa
room_description: Madame Antinori is a psychic for the town of Swannhaven. Rumor has it she started to dabble in Black Magic and accidentally cursed herself and her house. The whole house vanished with her in it. Lost to another realm for over 20 years, the house only appears for 60 minutes in random places. Now your group is locked in her house and only has 60 minutes to find her spell book to break the curse and get out or be trapped in darkness forever.
